description: Indicates study order presented to participant
Index of trial, increases by 1 for each subsequent trial
Indicates image shown on left-hand side of screen
Indicates image shown in central screen area (not used)
Indicates image shown on right-hand side of sreen
Indicates side of screen target appears, l = Left, r = Right
Indicates type of trial, mixed-language or single-language
Indicates participant's response, D = Looking at Distractor, T = Looking at Target, A = Looking Away
Duration of first shift (in # of frames) from distracter to target or from target to distracter
Indicates participant's reaction time in ms
